{"tid":568448,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PS2/SS 想搵返隻舊戰棋game","createTime":"2018-02-21T19:32:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T09:51:49.000Z","uid":172830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8830fc9eb54227d35f4ffdd7c5af241c30d89658","tid":568448,"uid":172830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T19:32:41.000Z","msg":"麻煩一下各位幫手，想搵隻好舊既戰棋game..已經唔太記得係SS定PS2<br />\n大致風格同 傭兵傳說 年代記 非常相似<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/79/7c3db798dc0675beadc5dde6590zmbb4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F79%2F7c3db798dc0675beadc5dde6590zmbb4.JPG&h=e1fc7074&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n遊戲特點有:<br />\n1.不是回合制,而係用每一隻角色行動值高低去決定邊隻角色行動先。所以敵我會交錯行動。<br />\n2.地形好似上圖咁有高低.會影響命中率同阻擋遠程攻擊。<br />\n3.攻擊時會有條識移動既bar,去到紅色區會爆擊(好似)，而攻擊時可以選擇另一個攻擊MODE.會將敵人打飛。<br />\n4.每個角色移動完可以選擇佢面向邊一個方向.會影響命中同格擋,所以一般都繞背打。而有個特別MODE下面講。<br />\n5.死左既敵人可以拎佢身上物品。<br />\n6.最特別就係有一個COMBO模式。如果將敵人打飛出去.佢撞到另一個角色.個角色係處於特別MODE.就會再將佢撞出去.即係話你有十個角色.全部用特別MODE排成一直線..個敵人會一直向前飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,最後會顯示你COMBO左幾多次,攻擊會倍化,掉落物品/武器都會更好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就好似咁:<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/037a0a297306fcc9fe4cca8b60bc6577.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F037a0a297306fcc9fe4cca8b60bc6577.jpg&h=238b26c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7.佢會有個類似勇者塔..比你打主線唔夠揪個陣.入塔練LV，可以一直打到好高層練新角色LV順便偷敵人D勁武器比你打主線，如果無記錯,隻GAME D武器幾乎都靠偷敵人個D拎返黎.因為敵人個D會勁D<br />\n8.佢有個僱傭兵系統.大部分戰友都係個度請返黎,再拎入塔度升級。<br />\n9.有個僱傭兵角色係小偷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大致係記得咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992972783bfb6667352d7fea2d467f47a8a97a0f","tid":568448,"uid":55029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T19:34:19.000Z","msg":"魔界戰記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"539092468b1496b14acae73bb495feb51a7b2b32","tid":568448,"uid":172830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T19:34:40.000Z","msg":"個勇者塔每幾十層就有CKECK POINT,等你輸左下次再打唔洗由頭打過"},{"pid":"aa81eeb81dbf89a565ee0a7d1ea37a04d206938f","tid":568448,"uid":172830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"992972783bfb6667352d7fea2d467f47a8a97a0f","tid":568448,"uid":55029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T19:34:19.000Z","msg":"魔界戰記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T19:36:52.000Z","msg":"非也，唔該哂先。"},{"pid":"6df865edaa62ad0804e64870f73215bff6032613","tid":568448,"uid":172830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T22:23:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dcfd9856753668da433b5bab30ddde3da6e020d","tid":568448,"uid":94835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T22:53:03.000Z","msg":"google image search ps2/ss srpg 慢慢搵"},{"pid":"ecc56c6520d8d0e5dd02797f398a1592a27c7f39","tid":568448,"uid":172830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dcfd9856753668da433b5bab30ddde3da6e020d","tid":568448,"uid":94835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T22:53:03.000Z","msg":"google image search ps2/ss srpg 慢慢搵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T05:31:29.000Z","msg":"搵過啦.. 哩D咁基本既關鍵字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb3290ce5fd663dcb05d584e42ea88329147760a","tid":568448,"uid":172830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T06:11:27.000Z","msg":"屌我搵到啦...好撚感動..真係搵左幾年...<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b_BQpsnfLfY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Db_BQpsnfLfY&d=2oBHitOUiWjcD5z7xhq%2FddZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=486bc213\" target=\"_blank\">https: